SELECT city_name, land_area_sq_miles, residential_area_sq_miles, commercial_area_sq_miles FROM population_demographics JOIN land_use ON population_demographics.city_name = land_use.city_name WHERE residential_area_sq_miles > 10 AND commercial_area_sq_miles > 5;

SELECT city_name, median_age, population, land_area_sq_miles FROM population_demographics JOIN land_use ON population_demographics.city_name = land_use.city_name WHERE population > 50000 AND land_area_sq_miles < 50 ORDER BY land_area_sq_miles ASC;

SELECT city_name, population, median_income, residential_area_sq_miles, agricultural_area_sq_miles FROM population_demographics JOIN land_use ON population_demographics.city_name = land_use.city_name WHERE agricultural_area_sq_miles > 2 ORDER BY population DESC;
